Local dev:

1) Run npm start in statics directory
2) Run npm start in frontend directory
3) localhost:3000

To create a new article:

1) Create raw .html files in src/articles
2) Create og file in src/templates
3) Create .html file in src referencing the og
4) Add HtmlWebPackPlug for main article file
5) Add HtmlWebPackPlugin rules for raw articles files in webpack.config.js (for both EN and DE)
6) Title image goes into statics directory (should be jpg and 650 width)
7) Article assets go into statics/{new directory}
8) Create the entry in articles table (needs a title, subtext and key)
9) Frontend and Statics builds are required on TC
